content: The last versions of Print House developed by Corel were Print House 2000 for the Macintosh and Print House 6 for Windows (2003).
NOTE: CPH files cannot be opened by most versions of CorelDRAW.

description: Printing project created with Corel Print House, a desktop publishing program; used for designing scrapbooks, greeting cards, banners, calendars, invitations, and printable documents.
